---
title: Golden Crumbed Chick'n & Apple Slaw Burger with Burger Sauce & Fries
description: Plant-based chicken is glowing in a burger, so we’re not going to hold back. Really make burger night shine with burger
sauce and a sweet apple slaw. Don’t forget the golden oven-baked fries!
